{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/5kfe50bq","slide":1,"text":"01","textPreview":"01","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[1180,674,36,20]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/sz1fng","slide":1,"text":"Onside is a trustless football prediction market built on Solana. Fans can bet on match outcomes, goals, cards, corners, and same-match combinations—but no administrator gets to decide the winner. Every result is verified using cryptographic data from TxODDS."}
