{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/prvj6w","slide":3,"text":"Onside gives fans a familiar sportsbook experience. They connect a wallet, choose YES or NO across markets, and can combine outcomes into one same-match ticket. Individual markets use shared parimutuel pools, so users do not need to find a direct counterparty. Their stake joins the pool, and winners share the payout."}
