{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/ltu16f","slide":5,"text":"Onside is already deployed end-to-end on Solana devnet: a working consumer interface, shared parimutuel pools, permissionless proof submission, and public settlement receipts. It turns TxODDS verified sports data into a prediction market that fans can understand and anyone can audit. Onside: the result is proven, not trusted."}